		   <br /><nobr><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=dethbringre&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>I was playing my bard last night, kiting of course , i had just finished a nice kite of about 10 mobs and i was bragging to my guild about it and one of the higher lvl bards said that kiting had been nerfed mid and high lvls.&nbsp;&nbsp;Im only 20 so i wouldnt know if it has been nerfed or not, i was just wandering if the devs nerfed our ability to solo, or if bards can still AE kite and swarm kite 15 or 20 mobs at a time?</p>
<br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />gamer... <br /> <br />Dethbringre 31 rogue Mannoroth</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >5 Replies</td></tr></table>
